Definition: a state of extreme poverty or destitution
Example: their indigence appalled him; a general state of need exists among the homeless
Synonyms: adj, all, poor, indigent, need, needy, penury, penurious, pauperism, pauperization, verb, possession, pauperize, poverty, a, state, of, extreme, or, destitution, their, appalled, him, general, exists, among, the, homeless
Category: noun.state
